Package: askha
Title: Agrobiodiversity Indexes to determine conservation status of crop cultivars
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c( 
          person("Omar", "Benites-Alfaro", email = "o.benites@metrika.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
          person("Vilma", "Hualla", , "v.hualla@cgiar.org", "aut"),
          person("Stef", "De Han", , "S.DeHaan@cgiar.org", "aut"),
          person(family = "Metrika Group", role = c("ctb")),
          person(family = "International Potato Center", role = c("ctb", "cph"))
          )
Maintainer: Omar Benites Alfaro <o.benites@metrika.org>
Description: Implementation of the RCF and OCF indices to measure abundance and evenness of agro-biodiversity in cultivars in sampled or monitored landscapes. RCF and OCF stand for Relative Cultivar Frequency and Overall Cultivar Frequency respectively.
